data.description: Wow! Loved & Maintained Single Family Home with impact glass windows, extended brick paver driveway, plantation shutters, fans, lighting & white privacy fenced yard with large screened patio! Granite Counters, LVP floors, open & inviting home includes all stainless steel appliance & washer / dryer, ring doorbell, backyard lighting & shed. Even the 2nd bathroom has a deep JETTED TUB! Come RELAX in your beautiful new home & enjoy a great neighborhood with friendly neighbors & close to everything! Dining, Shopping, Boat ramps, Turnpike all within minutes, yet this home is tucked in a quiet area! Everything is ready for you and NO HOMEOWNERS ASSOCIATION! Zillow has a walk-thru video.
